t-pool-300x249.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 577px) 100vw, 577px\" \/><\/a><br \/>\nThe drive back along the A8, looking out to Cannes  was a joy and before we knew it we were back at <strong><a title=\"French Riviera Bed and Breakfast\" href=\"www.villa-aurita.com\" target=\"_blank\">Villa Aurita (our  French Riviera Bed and Breakfast)<\/a> <\/strong>sipping a glass of our favourite ros\u00e9 on the terrace from UK owned winery <a title=\"Chateau Leoube\" href=\"http:\/\/www.chateauleoube.com\/en\/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chateau L\u00e9oube<\/strong>. <\/a> It had been hardwork but we had enjoyed every minute of it. Boy oh boy do I love my job (and Chef Lucy!)<\/p>\n<p><a title=\"Red Radish Taster Menu\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/2012\/06\/private-villa-catering-taster-menu\/\"><strong>Check out our Proven\u00e7al taster menu here.<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Was Chef Lucy that mean? Of course she wasn&#8217;t and it is safe to say that the clients absolutely loved the food and as they enthused at every dish, Lucy&#8230; <a class=\"more-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/red-radish-the-best-restaurant-on-the-french-riviera\/\"><span class=\"button button-outline button-dark\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\"> read more <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\"><\/i><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1956,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[11],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1955","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-latest-blog-postings"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Red Radish - The best &#039;Restaurant&#039; on the French Riviera. - Red Radish<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow,